on Charter Township]]\n*[[Milford Township, Michigan|Milford Charter Township]]\n*[[Oakland Charter Township, Michigan|Oakland Charter Township]]\n*[[Orion Township, Michigan|Orion Charter Township]]\n*[[Oxford Charter Township, Michigan|Oxford Charter Township]]\n*[[Royal Oak Charter Township, Michigan|Royal Oak Charter Township]]\n*[[Springfield Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Springfield Charter Township]]\n*[[Waterford Township, Michigan|Waterford Charter Township]]\n*[[West Bloomfield Township, Michigan|West Bloomfield Charter Township]]\n*[[White Lake Township, Michigan|White Lake Charter Township]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Civil townships===\n*[[Addison Township, Michigan|Addison Township]]\n*[[Groveland Township, Michigan|Groveland Township]]\n*[[Holly Township, Michigan|Holly Township]]\n*[[Novi Township, Michigan|Novi Township]]\n*[[Rose Township, Oakland County, Michigan|Rose Township]]\n*[[Southfield Township, Michigan|Southfield Township]]\n\n===Unincorporated communities===\n{{div col|colwidth=12em}}\n*[[Andersonville, Michigan|Andersonville]]\n*[[Austin Corners, Michigan|Austin Corners]]\n*[[Brandon Gardens, Michigan|Brandon Gardens]]\n*[[Campbells Corner, Michigan|Campbells Corner]]\n*[[Charing Cross, Michigan|Charing Cross]]\n*[[Clintonville, Michigan|Clintonville]]\n*[[Clyde, Michigan|Clyde]]\n*[[Commerce, Michigan|Commerce]]\n*[[Davisburg, Michigan|Davisburg]]\n*[[Drayton Plains, Michigan|Drayton Plains]]\n*[[East Highland, Michigan|East Highland]]\n*[[Elizabeth Lake, Michigan|Elizabeth Lake]]\n*[[Five Points, Oakland County, Michigan|Five Points]]\n*[[Four Towns, Michigan|Four Towns]]\n*[[Gingellville, Michigan|Gingellville]]\n*[[Glengary, Michigan|Glengary]]\n*[[Goodison, Michigan|Goodison]]\n*[[Groveland Corners, Michigan|Groveland Corners]]\n*[[Hickory Ridge, Michigan|Hickory Ridge]]\n*[[Highland, Michigan|Highland]]\n*[[Huron Heights, Michigan|Huron Heights]]\n*[[Jossman Acres, Michigan|Jossman Acres]]\n*[[Kensington, Michigan|Kensington]]\n